## 14. Open Questions

- What is the minimum viable data quality threshold?  
- Which messaging channel drives highest engagement?  
- How much control vs automation do agents prefer?  

---

## 15. Launch Plan

- Target early adopters (top-performing agents)  
- Offer white-glove onboarding  
- Collect case studies  
- Iterate on engagement + ROI  

---

## 16. Summary

ReconnectAI transforms static CRMs into active relationship engines by delivering timely, personalized insights at scale—unlocking a high-ROI, underutilized revenue stream for agents.

